OL,3,CNo funeral sector regulation means
OL,4,Cdead bodies can be kept in garages -
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FFuneral directors could work at home
OL,8,Fand keep bodies of dead people in
OL,9,Ftheir garages, an inquiry chairman
OL,10,Fwarned, as he called for a regulator
OL,11,Fto police the sector.
OL,13,FSir Jonathan Michael, who is
OL,14,Finvestigating how people who have died
OL,15,Fare looked after around the country in
OL,16,Fthe wake of necrophiliac killer David
OL,17,FFuller's mortuary abuse, found funeral
OL,18,Fdirectors do not need a licence,
OL,19,Fqualifications or training, and
OL,20,Fdescribed the sector is an
OL,21,F"unregulated free-for-all".
