OL,3,CNo funeral sector regulation means
OL,4,Cdead bodies can be kept in garages -
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FHe said many people are "shocked" to
OL,8,Ffind that the industry goes unchecked
OL,9,Fand anyone can set themselves up as a
OL,10,Ffuneral director.
OL,12,FPublishing his latest findings on
OL,13,FTuesday, he urged the Government to
OL,14,Fbring in a regulator for funeral
OL,15,Fdirectors in England as a "matter of
OL,16,Furgency".
