OL,3,CNo funeral sector regulation means
OL,4,Cdead bodies can be kept in garages -
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"There are no organisations in England
OL,8,Fwith the power to prevent funeral
OL,9,Fdirectors operating on the basis of
OL,10,Fpoor practice or neglect not deemed to
OL,11,Fbe criminal.
OL,13,F"We need a regime that will not
OL,14,Ftolerate any form of abuse or any
OL,15,Fpractices that compromise the security
OL,16,Fand dignity of the deceased," he said.
