OL,7,FThe Government launched the public
OL,8,Finquiry after the maintenance worker
OL,9,Fsexually abused the bodies of more
OL,10,Fthan a hundred women and girls aged
OL,11,Fbetween nine and 100 while employed at
OL,12,Fthe now-closed Kent and Sussex
OL,13,FHospital and the Tunbridge Wells
OL,14,FHospital, in Pembury, between 2005 and
OL,15,F2020.
