OL,4,Cdead bodies can be kept in garages -
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe first phase of the inquiry, which
OL,8,Flooked at his employer Maidstone and
OL,9,FTunbridge Wells NHS Trust, found
OL,10,FFuller was able to offend for 15 years
OL,11,Fwithout being caught due to "serious
OL,12,Ffailings" at the hospitals he worked
OL,13,Fat.
OL,15,FSir Jonathan said the latest report
OL,16,Ffollows "distressing" allegations of
OL,17,Fneglect as police investigate a
OL,18,Ffuneral directors in Hull.
