OL,3,CNo funeral sector regulation means
OL,4,Cdead bodies can be kept in garages -
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FHumberside Police said detectives had
OL,8,Fbeen working "around the clock" since
OL,9,Fconcerns were raised at Legacy
OL,10,FIndependent Funeral Directors in March
OL,11,F"about the storage and management
OL,12,Fprocesses relating to care of the
OL,13,Fdeceased at the funeral directors".
OL,15,FThe inquiry chairman said it was
OL,16,F"right and proper" that looking into
OL,17,FFuller "led to questions about the
OL,18,Fsecurity and dignity of the deceased
OL,19,Fin other settings".
