OL,3,CNo funeral sector regulation means
OL,4,Cdead bodies can be kept in garages -
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FSetting out how the regulator should
OL,8,Fhave the power to issue licences,
OL,9,Fdemand compulsory standards, inspect
OL,10,Ffuneral directors and take enforcement
OL,11,Faction, Sir Jonathan said he hopes
OL,12,Fpublishing the report will help
OL,13,Fministers and funeral homes to "take
OL,14,Fsteps that assure the public that the
OL,15,Fsector is fit for purpose and will not
OL,16,Ftolerate any form of abuse or practice
OL,17,Fwhich compromises the security and
OL,18,Fdignity of the deceased, including
OL,19,Fthat caused by neglect".
