OL,3,CNo funeral sector regulation means
OL,4,Cdead bodies can be kept in garages -
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FIt should be mandatory for customers
OL,8,Fto be given information about how
OL,9,Ffuneral directors will care for their
OL,10,Floved ones and what measures are in
OL,11,Fplace to protect them so the industry
OL,12,Fis more transparent in how it
OL,13,Foperates, the report added.
OL,15,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said
OL,16,Fthe Government was "committed to
OL,17,Fpreventing any similar atrocities
OL,18,Fhappening again and ensuring that the
OL,19,Fdeceased are safeguarded and treated
OL,20,Fwith dignity".
